# Google Search Console verification token.
# 1. Go to https://search.google.com/search-console
# 2. Add property "https://www.nileshpatil6.com" using URL prefix
# 3. Choose "HTML tag" verification method
# 4. Copy the value of content="..." from the meta tag
# 5. Paste it below (just the token, not the full meta tag)
# 6. Add the same variable on your hosting provider (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=
